text: Château-Gontier-sur-Mayenne () is a commune in the Mayenne department in north-western France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Château-Gontier (the seat), Azé and Saint-Fort.Arrêté préfectoral 14 November 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Mayenne department ==References== * INSEE commune file Category:Communes of Mayenne Category:Subprefectures in France
title: Château-Gontier-sur-Mayenne
